/******************************************************************
[Function Name] : APP_init                                        *
[Description]   : Does All the initialization Required for the    *
                  application to start including creating the     *
                  tasks and initializing the peripherals          *
[Args]:         : NOTHING                                         *
[in]            : NOTHING                                         *
[out]           : NOTHING                                         *
[in/out]        : NOTHING                                         *
[Returns]       : void                                            *
*******************************************************************/
