/******************************************************************
[Function Name] : APP_start                                       *
[Description]   : Starts the application                          *
[Args]:         : NOTHING                                         *
[in]            : NOTHING                                         *
[out]           : NOTHING                                         *
[in/out]        : NOTHING                                         *
[Returns]       : void                                            *
*******************************************************************/
void APP_start(void);


